text: Wang Xiaoyuan (born 12 May 1968) is a Chinese badminton player. She competed in mixed doubles at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of China Category:Badminton players at the 1996 Summer Olympics
